high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter where the coffee machine is.
Pick up the scoop on the counter.
Turn right and face the sink on the counter.
Rinse the scoop off in the sink, then turn off the water and pick the scoop back up.
Turn around and go to the diagonal part of the opposite counter.
Open up the second drawer from the left and place the scoop in the drawer, then close it.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off the scoop on the counter and place in the drawer across from the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward then turn right to face the counter left of the sink
Pick up the large spoon from the counter
Turn right and walk to the kitchen sink
Wash the spoon under water in the sink then remove it
Turn around and walk forward to the opposite counter
Open the top drawer second from the left and put the spoon in it
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned spoon in the kitchen drawer

high_descs: Turn right and go straight to the end of the counter, then turn right to face the counter with the coffee maker.
Pick up the large spoon from the counter.
Go to the sink to your right.
Wash the large spoon inside the sink.
Turn around and go to the counter in front of you.
Open the second drawer to the right, put the large spoon inside, then close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean large spoon in the drawer.
